4Geeks Academy offers a Course in Applied Artificial Intelligence designed for professionals aiming to integrate AI into their work. Over six weeks, participants will learn about various types of generative AI, context, prompts, and models through two live online classes per week. The course has a maximum class size of 12 attendees and requires no prior experience. Upon completion, students receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by multiple institutions. This program empowers participants to strategically implement AI to enhance their productivity and workplace capabilities. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop